overview:
We propose numerous items such as deep seating chairs, loveseats, sofas for which you can add a table or an ottoman. Our furniture is made of aluminum cast, resin wicker, glass, acrylic and exotic wood (Teak, Ipe, Brazilian cherry).

Selections for cushions and accessory pillows are substantial and made of « Sunbrella » acrylic fabrics. We also can provide you with custom-made pillows and protective covers.

In order to guarantee a great variety, our collections are harmonized: whether it is the exterior table, chair or living room that you prefer. Most patio furniture is manufactured in United States and North America by renowned manufacturers.
